nodes.text: This Quarren lived on the ocean-covered planet of Dac during the Battle of Mon Cala around 21 BBY.

Before the Battle of Mon Cala, this Quarren along with others participated in the meeting between their species and the Mon Calamari in the Mon Calamari City. During the meeting, this Quarren and two others expressed their opinions regarding the choosing of a new king (after the previous king, Yos Kolina, was assassinated) which they believed should not be Mon Calamari prince Lee-Char, but a Quarren.
